0.4.1
 - Fixed a bug - removed sniffing for IE and over-writing of the global getElementById method since this was causing errors in IE9
 - Optimized loop in the look function by reducing DOM queries for an element

0.4.0
  - Updated to use plugin API for RequireJS 0.24.0

0.3.0
  - Callback for a cssp dependency now receives a ref to the injected link DOM
    node as its argument.

0.2.0
  - Added support for cssp! module ID's in the requireJS paths configuration.
  - Added support for tracking css file injections, so same stylesheet is only
  ever loaded once.

0.0.1
  - Initial release: Support dependency on CSS files in RequireJS.
